  "title": "Turtle Soup",
  "statement": "A man entered a restaurant and ordered turtle soup. After one sip, he asked the waiter, 'Is this really turtle soup?' The waiter replied, 'Yes, it is definitely turtle soup.' That night, the man took his own life. Why?",
